name: FaYoh
overview: The Super Mario Bros/Giana Sisters colorful clone from NC.Gamez. "FaYoh" is a bit of an odd title. Here's the backstory: "Scooter" is a popular German eurodance band. "Fire" is one of their biggest hits. Due to the singer's heavy accent, he seems to be constantly yelling "FaYoh" during the song. NC. Gamez thought that was funny and decided to pay homage to it.
